id: pm-2a9n
title: Refresh CodeQL Actions and reject incompatible Node 26 type-contract bump
description: "Update both CodeQL action steps in lockstep to v4.37.0 at the official immutable commit SHA, take the safe @types/node 22.20.1 patch, and reject Dependabot PR #462 Node 26 declarations because the runtime contract remains Node >=22.18.0. Verify workflow, type, coverage, security, and package gates."
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[4]: codeql,dependencies,github-actions,typescript
created_at: "2026-07-10T09:40:10.713Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-10T10:14:23.217Z"
closed_at: "2026-07-10T10:14:21.780Z"
author: codex-root
resolution: completed
expected_result: "Keep CodeQL init/analyze pinned in lockstep to official v4.37.0, retain type-level enforcement of the Node 22 minimum runtime, and pass every required quality gate."
actual_result: CodeQL v4.37.0 resolves to commit 99df26d4f13ea111d4ec1a7dddef6063f76b97e9; @types/node updates safely from 22.20.0 to 22.20.1 while the incompatible 26.x major is rejected. Typecheck and workflow contracts pass after the correction.
